  "full_text": "An update for lvm2 is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe lvm2 packages include complete support for handling read and write operations on physical volumes, creating volume groups from one or more physical volumes, and creating one or more logical volumes in volume groups.Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s): RHEL 8.10 after upgrade lvraid1 LV's that had intergity before now fail to setup integrity.  (JIRA:RHEL-118797)"
